
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-sengul-ace-mqtt-tls-profile-04.txt'>
    <title>"MQTT-TLS profile of ACE", Cigdem Sengul, Anthony Kirby, Paul Fremantle</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-sengul-ace-mqtt-tls-profile-04.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies a profile for the ACE (Authentication and Authorization for Constrained Environments) to enable authorization in an MQTT-based publish-subscribe messaging system.  Proof-of- possession keys, bound to OAuth2.0 access tokens, are used to authenticate and authorize publisher and subscriber clients.  The protocol relies on TLS for confidentiality and server authentication.</description>
    <dc:date>2019-04-06T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
